        </p>
        <p>
            <b>&lt;ToolstripButton/&gt;</b> is the button control for toolstrips and ribbons.
            It respons to the <b>Large</b>, <b>Small</b> and <b>Icon</b> size in <b>&lt;RibbonButtons/&gt;</b>.
        </p>
        <p>
            Please check out
            <a href="/gacui/components/controls/toolstrip/toolstripbutton.html">
                Toolstrip Controls
            </a>
            for details about using <b>&lt;ToolstripButton/&gt;</b>.
            Toolstrip buttons in toolstrip controls and ribbon controls have exactly same functionalities.
            Ribbon controls only provide more themes.
        </p>
